{"tid":1552323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請立即停止屌前線","createTime":"2019-09-08T10:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T11:59:43.000Z","uid":71253,"like":133,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"daa2aabc89ef59ddfdb0a63eabab41a9e9da28ec","tid":1552323,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"由狗係中環亂捉人開始就已經係場大龍鳳黎<br />\n前線手足見到有狗扮人set rb以為係手足去幫手都正常<br />\n放火係狗一啲都唔出奇<br />\n如果大家仲係金鐘就去提佢地今日遊行既目的<br />\n相信真手足都會明白同離開<br />\n<br />\n你地一黎就屌前線係冇任何意義<br />\n佢地聽唔到之餘<br />\n亦只係分化緊手足<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62e69446ceb4e9b946137725f13a04ea4887344","tid":1552323,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5d434f337116c36d319c1703f16069a595f278","tid":1552323,"uid":71253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6889de68f1dc86cdc18923e4aeae6fe9fd454daa","tid":1552323,"uid":122413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>美領最安全!<br />\n美領最安全!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">班狗就係因為唔敢係美領附近開波</span><br />\n先會出招混亂拉人同封站<br />\n目標令到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">引起混亂</span></strong>大家唔去美領同SPIN走明天新聞重點!<br />\n唔好中計!由班狗係罰企一日!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">另外絕不分化前線!不割席!</span><br />\n但美領一定要多人!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><